bridge%2C%20citing%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20the%20current%20boat%20transportation%20system.%20Presently%2C%20travelling%20across%20the%20Brahmaputra%20by%20boat%20can%20take%20three%20to%20four%20hours%2C%20with%20significant%20disruptions%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season.%20The%20new%20bridge%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20the%20travel%20distance%20between%20Dhubri%20and%20Phulwari%20by%20around%20200%20kilometres%2C%20streamlining%20trade%20and%20other%20essential%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20bridge%20gets%20built%2C%20the%20benefit%20will%20be%20that%20we%20can%20reach%20Meghalaya%20in%20a%20much%20shorter%20time.%20It%20will%20make%20things%20easier%20for%20businesses%20since%20transporting%20goods%20on%20boats%20is%20very%20challenging.%20With%20the%20bridge%2C%20it%20will%20be%20much%20easier.%20It%20takes%20three%20hours%20by%20boat%2C%20so%20this%20bridge%20will%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20also%20shared%20his%20reviews%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20bridge%20is%20completed%2C%20it%20will%20help%20us%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20like%20in%20coordination%20because%20it%20takes%20a%20long%20time%20to%20travel%20by%20boat%2C%20approximately%203%20hours.%20Also%2C%20it's%20a%20huge%20river%2C%20which%20is%20dangerous%20too.%20Dhubri%20and%20Meghalaya%2C%20both%20states%2C%20will%20benefit%20from%20this%20bridge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bridge's%20significance%20has%20become%20a%20central%20theme%20in%20the%20electoral%20campaigns%20of%20the%20three%20competing%20parties.%20Each%20party%20claims%20credit%20for%20initiating%20or%20championing%20the%20project%2C%20with%20differing%20narratives%20on%20its%20origins.%20Javed%20Islam%20of%20the%20AGP%2C%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20emphasised%20the%20role%20of%20the%20current%20central%20government%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20NDA%20government%20started%20the%20work%20of%20this%20bridge.%20In%202021%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20this%20bridge%2C%20and%20the%20construction%20is%20progressing%20rapidly.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20significant%20gift%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Assam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBadruddin%20Ajmal%2C%20the%20AIUDF%20president%20and%20a%20three-time%20MP%20from%20Dhubri%2C%20asserted%20that%20the%20bridge%20was%20a%20result%20of%20his%20efforts%2C%20claiming%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20raised%20this%20issue%20in%20Parliament%20during%20the%20Congress%20government%20and%20then%20during%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20ensuring%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20received%20this%20gift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20has%20also%20highlighted%20its%20contributions%2C%20mentioning%20the%20bridge%20in%20its%20campaign%20rallies%20to%20secure%20credit.%20Despite%20the%20political%20debate%2C%20the%20consensus%20among%20locals%20is%20that%20the%20bridge%20is%20essential%20and%20will%20significantly%20improve%20their%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20competing%20narratives%20continue%20to%20unfold%20as%20election%20day%20approaches%2C%20the%20Dhubri%20Phulwari%20Bridge%20remains%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20and%20Meghalaya%2C%20symbolising%20progress%20and%20connectivity%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECampaigning%20for%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20polls%20in%20four%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20in%20Assam%20scheduled%20on%20May%207%20ended%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2047%20candidates%2C%20including%20one%20sitting%20MP%20and%20four%20sitting%20MLAs%2C%20are%20in%20the%20fray%20for%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20polls%20in%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%3A%20Guwahati%2C%20Kokrajhar%2C%20Barpeta%20and%20Dhubri%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E14%20candidates%20are%20in%20the%20fray%20in%20Barpeta%20seat%20while%2C%2013%20candidates%20are%20contesting%20