r%2098%20runs%20in%20just%20eight%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20runs%20to%20be%20scored%20in%20the%20second%20innings.%20When%20you%20are%20chasing%20a%20big%20total%2C%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20go%20too%20hard%20and%20you%20end%20up%20losing%20wickets.%20Just%20a%20poor%20performance%20overall.%20We%20didn't%20(hit%20our%20lengths%20consistently)%2C%20just%20had%20a%20poor%20performance%20overall%20with%20bat%2C%20ball%20and%20in%20the%20field.%20Sunil%20Narine%20and%20Phil%20Salt%2C%20in%20the%20powerplay%2C%20we've%20seen%20how%20they%20bat%20and%20they%20do%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20the%20opposition.%20Our%20young%20bowlers%20couldn't%20handle%20that%20kind%20of%20pressure%20and%20he%20hit%20some%20really%20good%20shots%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20said%20after%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20LSG%20looked%20clueless%20against%20hard-hitting%20Narine%2C%20Rahul%20stated%20that%20they%20had%20plans%20to%20deal%20with%20KKR%20batters%20but%20got%20the%20execution%20part%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20prepare%20well%20in%20advance%20and%20talk%20about%20the%20opposition%20batters%2C%20we%20know%20our%20conditions%20here%20and%20we%20do%20spend%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time%20talking%20to%20the%20bowlers%20and%20talking%20to%20the%20batters%20trying%20to%20see%20what%20kind%20of%20plans%20we%20need%20to%20come%20up%20with.%20Once%20we%20come%20here%2C%20it's%20about%20execution%20and%20we%20went%20wrong%20in%20that%20part.%20Bowlers%20tried%20their%20best%20but%20the%20young%20group%20really%20...%20the%20sooner%20you%20learn%2C%20the%20better%20it%20for%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20game%2C%20LSG%20opted%20to%20field%20first%20after%20winning%20the%20toss.%20Narine's%2081%2C%20combined%20with%20solid%20knocks%20from%20Phil%20Salt%20(32%20in%2014%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%2C%20Angkrish%20Raghuvanshi%20(32%20in%2026%20balls%2