or%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqantas-airlines-flights-australia-competition-consumer-commission-lawsuit-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EACCC%20accused%20Qantas%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20misleading%20customers%20by%20advertising%20tickets%20for%20over%208%2C000%20flights%20that%20had%20already%20been%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20regulators%20alleged%20that%20the%20airline%20kept%20the%20tickets%20up%20for%20sale%20online%20for%20an%20average%20of%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20flights%20were%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20allege%20that%20Qantas'%20conduct%20in%20continuing%20to%20sell%20tickets%20to%20canceled%20flights%2C%20and%20not%20updating%20ticketholders%20about%20canceled%20flights%2C%20left%20customers%20with%20less%20time%20to%20make%20alternative%20arrangements%20and%20may%20have%20led%20to%20them%20paying%20higher%20prices%20to%20fly%20at%20a%20particular%20time%20not%20knowing%20that%20flight%20had%20already%20been%20canceled%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ACCC%20said%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQantas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qantasnewsroom.com.au%2Fmedia-releases%2Fqantas-update-on-accc-claims%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponded%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20did%20not%20%26quot%3Bdelay%20communicating%20with%20our%20passengers%20for%20commercial%20gain%26quot%3B%20or%20cancel%20flights%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20slots.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20is%20now%20agreeing%20to%20pay%20up%20to%20%2413.2%20million%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20settle%20the%20case%20brought%20by%20the%20ACCC.%20According%20to%20the%20ACCC%2C%20the%20payments%20to%20impacted%20customers%20will%20be%20in%20addition%20to%20any%20refunds%20or%20alternative%20flights%20that%20the%20airline%20may%20have%20already%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20paying%20customers%2C%20the%20airline%20agreed%20to%20pay%20a%20civil%20penalty%20of%20100%20million%20Australian%20dollars%20or%20%2466.1%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqantas-airways-settlement-customers-purchased-canceled-flights-accc-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714960300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66382f36b8f515beaf119eaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqantas-airways-settlement-customers-purchased-canceled-flights-accc-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Qantas%20Airways%20agreed%20to%20pay%20approximately%2020%20million%20Australian%20dollars%20to%20more%20than%2086%2C000%20customers%20who%20were%20sold%20tickets%20to%20canceled%20flights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqantas-airways-settlement-customers-purchased-canceled-flights-accc-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MBBS%20Student%20Appears%20As%20Proxy%20Candidate%20In%20NEET%2C%20Detained%20With%205%20Others%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20MBBS%20student%20who%20appeared%20in%20place%20of%20a%20NEET%20aspirant%20in%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20on%20Sunday%20was%20detained%20along%20with%20five%20others%2C%20including%20the%20candidate%2C%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Bharatpur%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreliminary%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20Abhishek%20Gupta%2C%20a%20government%20college%20student%2C%20was%20part%20of%20a%20racket%20being%20run%20by%20his%20collegemate%20Ravi%20Meena%2C%20who%20had%20allegedly%20taken%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20from%20candidate%20Rahul%20Gurjar%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20an%20examination%20centre%2C%20Abhishek%20was%20found%20impersonating%20Rahul%20Gurjar.%20On%20suspicion%2C%20the%20invigilator%20handed%20him%20over%20to%20th