nervous%20but%20has%20no%20jitters%20about%20flying%20in%20a%20new%20spacecraft.%20While%20training%20at%20the%20launch%20pad%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20reach%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20it%20will%20be%20like%20going%20back%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20to%20Dr%20Deepak%20Pandya%20and%20Bonnie%20Pandya%2C%20the%2059-year-old%20will%20create%20history%20by%20being%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20fly%20on%20a%20maiden%20mission%20of%20a%20new%20human-rated%20spacecraft.%20A%20qualified%20navy%20test%20pilot%2C%20she%20has%20flown%20twice%20to%20space%20in%202006%20and%202012%2C%20and%20according%20to%20data%20from%20NASA%2C%20%26quot%3BSunita%20has%20spent%20a%20cumulative%20total%20of%20322%20days%20in%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20time%20she%2C%20used%20to%20hold%20the%20record%20for%20maximum%20spacewalk%20time%20by%20a%20female%20astronaut%20as%20she%20has%20spent%2050%20hour%20and%2040%20minutes%20across%20seven%20spacewalks.%20NASA%20says%20while%20on%20board%20with%20seven%20space%20walks%20totalling%2050%20hours%20and%2040%20minutes%2C%20Sunita%20held%20the%20record%20for%20total%20cumulative%20spacewalk%20time%20by%20a%20female%20astronaut%20but%20that%20has%20since%20been%20overtaken%20by%20Peggy%20Whitson%20with%2010%20spacewalks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20Williams's%20father%20was%20a%20neuroanatomist%20born%20in%20Jhulasan%2C%20in%20Mehsana%20District%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20but%20later%20migrated%20to%20the%20USA%20and%20married%20Bonnie%20Pandya%2C%20a%20Slovenian.%20NASA%20says%20she%20is%20currently%20preparing%20to%20be%20the%20pilot%20of%20the%20Crew%20Flight%20Test%20mission%20aboard%20Boeing's%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20-%20the%20first%20crewed%20flight%20for%20that%20vehicle%20-%20and%20her%20third%20mission%20aboard%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%20She%20was%20selected%20to%20be%20an%20astronaut%20in%201998%2C%20and%20after%20the%20Space%20Shuttle%20was%20retired%20in%202015%2C%20she%20was%20chosen%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20select%20group%20of%20astronauts%20who%20would%20fly%20on%20NASA's%20commercial%20crew%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20her%20flight%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20had%20told%20NDTV%20that%20she%20will%20carry%20a%20statue%20of%20Lord%20Ganesh%20with%20her%20on%20the%20commercial%20crew%20flight%20as%20%26quot%3BGanesh%20is%20her%20good%20luck%20charm%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she%20was%20more%20spiritual%20than%20religious%20and%20was%20happy%20to%20have%20Lord%20Ganesh%20with%20her%20in%20outer%20space.%20On%20her%20earlier%20flights%2C%20she%20has%20carried%20copies%20of%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20to%20space.%20She%20also%20said%20she%20loved%20samosas!%20Among%20her%20other%20passions%2C%20she%20is%20also%20a%20marathon%20runner%20and%20ran%20a%20marathon%20while%20at%20the%20ISS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20its%20own%20human%20spaceflight%20program%2C%20the%20Gaganyaan%2C%20and%20the%20head%20of%20ISRO's%20Human%20Space%20Flight%20Center%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Dr.%20M%20Mohan%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BCaptain%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20a%20veteran%20of%20space%20missions%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20is%20embarking%20on%20another%20mission%20on%20the%20maiden%20flight%20of%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20craft%2C%20which%20makes%20us%20all%20proud.%20I%20wish%20Ms.%20Williams%20all%20success%20on%20another%20milestone%20journey%20to%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20selected%20a%20crew%20of%20four%20male%20Gaganyatris%2C%20and%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20they%20may%20fly%20into%20space%20from%20Sriharikota%20in%20the%20thereabouts%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20selected%20SpaceX%20and%20Boeing%20to%20make%20new%20spacecraft%20that%20would%20ferry%20astronauts%20to%20and%20from%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20and%20SpaceX%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20since%202020.%20The%20Boeing%20Starliner%20has%20had%20many%20delays%20and%20is%20now%20set%20for%20the%20maiden%20crewed%20flight%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%20Incidentally%2C%20Boeing%20has%20been%20facing%20many%20issues%20with%20its%20aircrafts%20and%20the%20company%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20will%20be%20flying%20alongside%2061-year-old%20Astronaut%20Barry%20Eugene%20%26quot%3BButch%26quot%3B%20Wilmore%2C%20a%20navy%20test%20pilot%20who%20has%20flown%20into%20space%20twice.%20Both%20veterans%20will%20be%20launching%20on%20a%20United%20Launch%20Alliance%20Atlas%20V%20rocket%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%20The%20astronauts%20will%20spend%20about%20a%20week%20at%20the%20orbiting%20laboratory%20before%20the%20crew%20capsule%20makes%20a%20parachute%20and%20airbag-assisted%20landing%20in%20the%20southwestern%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20says%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20was%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20name%20the%20spacecraft%20she%20would%20fly%20in%2C%20and%20she%20named%20it%20%26quot%3BCalypso%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20famous%20ship%20on%20which%20the%20French%20oceanographer%20and%20legendary%20filmmaker%20Jacques-Yves%20Cousteau%20explored%20the%20oceans%20when%20she%20was%20still%20a%20student.%20She%20also%20has%20a%20school%20named%20after%20her%2C%20the%20Sunita%20Williams%20Elementary%20School%2C%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Needham%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20and%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20she%20will%20interact%20with%20school%20children%20from%20aboard%20the%20space%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Boeing%2C%20the%20Crew%20Space%20Transportation%20(CST)-100%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20was%20designed%20to%20accommodate%20seven%20passengers%2C%20or%20a%20mix%20of%20crew%20and%20cargo%2C%20for%20missions%20to%20low-Earth%20orbit.%20It%20has%20been%20in%20the%20making%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20and%20has%20had%20many%20hiccups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20Williams%20says%20her%20days%20will%20be%20packed%20with%20fun%20activities%20(flying%20routines)%20as%20she%20is%20flying%20a%20mission%20to%20test%20and%20certify%20a%20new%20spacecraft.%20She%20is%20going%20to%20create%20history%20as%20she%20flies%20in%20the%20maiden%20mission%20of%20the%20new%20spacecraft%2C%20which%20has%20her%20fingerprints%20all%20over%20as%20she%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20its%20development%20along%20with%20Boeing%20and%20NASA%20engineers.%20With%20Lord%20Ganesh%20by%20her%20side%2C%20things%20should%20go%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714959960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-02%2Fsunita-williams_650x400_61456513868.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Findian-origin-astronaut-sunita-williams-set-to-fly-into-space-again-5593781%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Captain%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20who%20loves%20to%20eat%20samosas%20in%20space%2C%20is%20ready%20to%20fly%20into%20space%20once%20again%2C%20and%20this%20time%20on%20a%20brand-new%20spacecraft%2C%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Findian-origin-astronaut-sunita-williams-set-to-fly-into-space-again-5593781%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Findian-origin-astronaut-sunita-williams-set-to-fly-into-space-again-5593781%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Findian-origin-astronaut-sunita-williams-set-to-fly-into-space-again-5593781%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qantas%20To%20Pay%20%2466%20Million%20Fine%20After%20%26quot%3BGhost%20Flights%26quot%3B%20Scandal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralian%20airline%20Qantas%20agreed%20to%20pay%20a%20%2466%20million%20fine%20Monday%20after%20a%20bruising%20%26quot%3Bghost%20flights%26quot%3B%20scandal%2C%20following%20accusations%20it%20kept%20selling%20seats%20on%20long-cancelled%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20competition%20watchdog%20said%20Qantas%20%26quot%3Badmitted%20that%20it%20misled%20consumers%26quot%3B%20by%20advertising%20seats%20on%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20flights%20--%20despite%20those%20flights%20being%20cancelled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQantas%20will%20also%20fork%20out%20%2413%20million%20in%20compensation%20to%2086%2C000%20travellers%20impacted%20by%20the%20cancellations%20and%20botched%20rescheduling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQantas'%20conduct%20was%20egregious%20and%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Australian%20Competition%20and%20Consumer%20Commission%20chairperson%20Gina%20Cass-Gottlieb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20consumers%20will%20have%20made%20holiday%2C%20business%20and%20travel%20plans%20after%20booking%20on%20a%20phantom%20flight%20that%20had%20been%20cancelled.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQantas%20said%20that%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20customers%20were%20booked%20on%20flights%20that%20had%20been%20cancelled%20%26quot%3Btwo%20or%20more%26quot%3B%20days%20prior.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQantas%20chief%20executive%20Vanessa%20Hudson%20said%20the%20airline%20%26quot%3Blet%20down%20customers%20and%20fell%20short%20of%20our%20own%20standards%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20many%20of%20our%20customers%20were%20affected%20by%20our%20failure%20to%20provide%20cancellation%20notifications%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20and%20we%20are%20sincerely%20sorry%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2466%20million%20(Aus%24100%20million)%20fine%20is%20subject%20to%20court%20approval.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong-dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BSpirit%20of%20Australia%26quot%3B%2C%20103-year-old%20national%20carrier%20Qantas%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20repair%20its%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20faced%20a%20consumer%20backlash%20stirred%20up%20by%20soaring%20ticket%20prices%2C%20claims%20of%20sloppy%20service%20and%20the%20sacking%20of%201%2C700%20ground%20staff%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQantas%20has%20previously%20defended%20selling%20seats%20on%20cancelled%20flights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20argued%20that%20rather%20than%20buying%20tickets%20for%20specific%20seats%2C%20customers%20buy%20a%20%26quot%3Bbundle%20of%20rights%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20promise%20the%20airline%20will%20%26quot%3Bdo%20its%20best%20to%20get%20consumers%20where%20they%20want%20to%20be%20on%20time%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQantas%20posted%20an%20annual%20profit%20of%20%241.1%20billion%20last%20year%2C%20capping%20a%20major%20financial%20rebound%20after%20the%20travel%20turbulence%20of%20the%20Covid%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20chief%20executive%20Alan%20Joyce%20announced%20his%20early%20retirement%20amid%20a%20barrage%20of%20criticism%20in%20September%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714959900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Flp3o5qa8_-qantas-flight_625x300_31_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fqantas-to-pay-66-million-fine-after-ghost-flights-scandal-5597706%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australian%20airline%20Qantas%20agreed%20to%20pay%20a%20%2466%20million%20fine%20Monday%20after%20a%20bruising%20%26quot%3Bghost%20flights%26quot%3B%20scandal%2C%20following%20accusations%20it%20kept%20selling%20seats%20on%20long-cancelled%20trips.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fqantas-to-pay-66-million-fine-after-ghost-flights-scandal-5597706%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fqantas-to-pay-66-million-fine-after-ghost-flights-scanda