3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20by%20Perterson-KFF%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Kaiser%20Family%20Foundation)%20and%20based%20on%20data%20between%202018%20through%202020%2C%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20childbirth%20for%20an%20insured%20mother%20is%20%2418%2C865.%20While%20for%20insured%20mothers%20the%20majority%20of%20that%20is%20covered%2C%20out-of-pocket%20payments%20are%20still%20%242%2C852%2C%20on%20average.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20wife%20was%20ecstatic%20to%20be%20back%20in%20her%20country%20and%20getting%20help%20from%20her%20parents%20and%20sister%20with%20our%20son.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20would%20take%20our%20son%20for%20walks%20in%20his%20stroller%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fokinawa-blue-zone-and-its-longevity-secrets-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eolder%20Japanese%20men%20and%20women%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20would%20often%20smile%2C%20bend%20down%20low%20to%20get%20a%20close%20look%20at%20our%20son%2C%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3Bkawaii%20ne%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bhe's%20cute%20isn't%20he%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20Japanese.%20The%20warmth%20and%20feeling%20of%20safety%20on%20the%20street%20made%20us%20feel%20like%20we'd%20made%20the%20right%20decision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EDay%20care%20is%20affordable%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20son%20is%20now%20one%20and%20we've%20started%20talking%20about%20putting%20him%20in%20Houkien%2C%20government-subsidized%20day%20care%20for%20kids%205%20and%20under.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20Japanese%20government%20announced%20that%20by%202025%20day%20care%20for%20all%20children%206%20months%20to%202%20years%20old%20will%20be%20free%2C%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.japantimes.co.jp%2Fnews%2F2023%2F12%2F25%2Fjapan%2Fsociety%2Fnurseries-open-to-all-families%2F%5C%22%