gagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fnetanyahus-cabinet-votes-to-close-al-jazeera-offices-in-israel%2Farticleshow%2F109858035.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fnetanyahus-cabinet-votes-to-close-al-jazeera-offices-in-israel%2Famp_articleshow%2F109858035.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fnetanyahus-cabinet-votes-to-close-al-jazeera-offices-in-israel%2Famp_articleshow%2F109858035.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir%20Is%20Very%20Much%20A%20Part%20Of%20India%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20is%20part%20of%20India%20and%20added%20that%20there%20is%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20Indian%20Parliament%20which%20states%20that%20PoK%20is%20part%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20people%20were%20made%20to%20forget%20about%20PoK%2C%20however%2C%20it%20is%20now%20back%20in%20the%20consciousness%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20India's%20plans%20for%20PoK%20during%20an%20interactive%20session%20in%20Cuttack%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BPoK%20has%20never%20been%20out%20of%20this%20country.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20this%20country.%20There%20is%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20Indian%20Parliament%20that%20PoK%20is%20very%20much%20a%20part%20of%20India.%20Now%2C%20how%20did%20PoK%2C%20how%20did%20other%20people%20get%20control%3F%20You%20know%2C%20when%20you%20have%20someone%20who%20is%20not%20a%20responsible%20custodian%20of%20a%20house%2C%20someone%20steals%20from%20outside.%20Now%2C%20here%20you%20have%20allowed%20another%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20it%20was%20because%20we%20did%20not%20pursue%20the%20vacation%20of%20Pakistan%20from%20these%20territories%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20their%20independence%20that%20this%20very%20sorry%20state%20of%20affairs%20is%20continuing.%20So%2C%20what%20will%20happen%20in%20the%20future%3F%20Very%20difficult%20to%20tell.%20But%2C%20I%20always%20tell%20people%20one%20thing%20today%20PoK%20is%20in%20the%20consciousness%20once%20again%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20We%20had%20forgotten%20about%20it.%20We%20were%20made%20to%20forget%20about%20it.%20That%20it%20is%20today%20back%20definitely%2C%20the%20fact%20you%20are%20asking%20me%20a%20question%20is%2C%20I%20think%2C%20something%20which%20is%20very%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20stressed%20that%20it%20should%20have%20been%20abrogated%20a%20long%20time%20back.%20Jaishankar%20noted%20that%20a%20feeling%20of%20separatism%20and%20extremism%20existed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20when%20Article%20370%20remained%20in%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20critiques%20of%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20temporary%20provision%20in%20the%20constitution%20and%20it%20had%20to%20be%20removed.%20He%20stated%20that%20Article%20370%20continued%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20people%20had%20a%20vested%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20problem%20we%20had%20was%20Article%20370.%20It%20was%20a%20problem%20because%20so%20long%20as%20Article%20370%20continued%2C%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20a%20feeling%20of%20separatism%2C%20of%20extremism%2C%20sometimes%20I%20would%20even%20say%20support%20for%20violence%2C%20was%20created.%20This%20was%20done%20because%20of%20political%20interests%20of%20some%20parties%2C%20some%20parties%20at%20the%20center%20and%20some%20parties%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20this%20step%20which%20happened%20in%202019%20should%20have%20happened%20a%20long%20time%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20a%20Modi%20Sarkar%20till%20recently.%20And%20it%20was%20frankly%20an%20agenda%20that%20should%20have%20been%20done%20because%20it%20was%20a%20temporary%20provision%20of%20the%20constitution.%20You%20know%2C%20people%20debate%20saying%2C%20was%20it%20right%3F%20Was%20it%20wrong%3F%20In%20the%20constitution%2C%20it%20was%20written%20there%2C%20this%20is%20a%20temporary%20provision.%20What%20does%20temporary%20mean%3F%20That%20it%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%20This%20was%20to%20happen.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20was%20continued%20because%20people%20had%20vested%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20April%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20asserted%20that%20considering%20the%20development%20taking%20place%20in%20India%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%20will%20themselves%20demand%20to%20be%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20worry.%20PoK%20was%2C%20is%20and%20will%20remain%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20addressing%20a%20rally%20at%20West%20Bengal's%20Darjeeling%20on%20Sunday%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20had%20nominated%20sitting%20MP%20Raju%20Bista.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20power%20is%20increasing...India's%20prestige%20is%20increasing%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20our%20economy%20is%20fast%20progressing.%20Now%20our%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20in%20PoK%20will%20themselves%20demand%20to%20come%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714904940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flhp50aog_s-jaish