0are%20always%20willing%20to%20make%20exceptions.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20a%20family%20that%20has%20two%20kids%20and%20one%20is%20admitted%20here%20and%20the%20other%20is%20an%20infant%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20family%20to%20bring%20both%20kids%20so%20they%20can%20all%20live%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Girish%20shares.%20They%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20comfort%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327071%2Fvaranasi-ias-officer-himanshu-nagpal-mission-muskaan-reunites-lost-children-with-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20trumps%20everything%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20navigate%20this%20challenge%2C%20it%20is%20reassuring%20to%20know%20that%20someone%20is%20looking%20out%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECancer%20warrants%20a%20certain%20trepidation%2C%20a%20certain%20tiptoeing%2C%20a%20certain%20foreboding.%20But%20the%20laughter%20and%20happy%20chatter%20at%20the%20Access%20Life%20centres%2C%20disagree.%20For%20anyone%20looking%20in%2C%20there%20is%20only%20hope%20to%20be%20found%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20donate%20to%20their%20cause%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accesslife.org%2Fdonation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714733955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-1714468603.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankeet%20Dave%20and%20Girish%20Nair%2C%20founders%20of%20Access%20Life%2C%20were%20deeply%20affected%20by%20the%20pain%20of%20infants%20undergoing%20chemotherapy.%20They%20started%20helping%20the%20patients%E2%80%99%20families%20with%20shelter%2C%20food%2