0injured%20knee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virgin%20landscape%20boasts%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftags%2Fbest-treks-in-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20challenging%20steep%20climb%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Meenakshi%20Singh%20was%20unsure%20whether%20her%20knee%20could%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20terrain.%20When%20she%20was%20inclined%20to%20back%20out%2C%20the%20girls%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20hear%20of%20it%3B%20amping%20her%20positivity%20with%20every%20step%20she%20took.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticulating%20this%20%E2%80%9Conce-in-a-lifetime%E2%80%9D%20experience%2C%20Meenakshi%20says%20the%20girls%20in%20her%20group%20never%20gave%20up%20on%20her.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20almost%20pulled%20me%20half-way!%20One%20of%20them%20was%20carrying%20my%20bag%2C%20another%20giving%20me%20water%20at%20every%20few%20stops%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20we%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finish%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20group%20gathered%20around%20their%20hero%2C%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20this%20was%20a%20collective%20win.%20Cold%20water%20was%20relished%20at%20the%20top%20and%20biscuits%20were%20passed%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20day%2C%20the%20hills%20of%20Dzuko%20witnessed%20friendship%20at%20its%20best.%20And%20no%20one%20looking%20on%20would%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20that%20just%20a%20few%20days%20back%2C%20these%20girls%20had%20been%20strangers%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20what%20travel%20does%20to%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Zinal%20Doshi%2C%20leader%20of%20this%20iconic%20trek%20and%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Flapper%20Life%E2%80%99.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334177%2Fbest-travel-startups-in-india-local-experiences-tentgram-curtain-call-adventures-not-on-map%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiential%20trave